Hey guys! Are there any Harry Potter fans here? ⚡️
⠀
I’ve made a compilation of my Harry Potter series which I did in a filled-outline style. Not many of you remember this but I spent years working in that style and I still like it a lot even though I’ve moved away from it 👨‍🎨
⠀
I hope you will like watching this compilation and let me know if you want to see more illustrations in outline style from me. Thanks! 🤗

New chapter in my course! 🐦
⠀
Hi friends! I’m so happy to share a new speedpaint video with you. It took me a lot of time to create, because besides this 1 minute speedpaint I also prepared a step by step 2 hours length tutorial of how to do it from scratch for everyone who enrolled to my “Become a Pro in Procreate” course! 🎉
⠀
In this new chapter, we will create a flying bird animation step by step. You will learn new techniques of creating looped animations and a bunch of tips on how to create animations in Procreate faster. Together we will design a bird character, set up its movement, and finalize the animation by adding some little details, fxs and clouds in the background ☁️
⠀
If you have an iPad and want to create your own version of this cute bird, I encourage you to enroll to my “Become a Pro in Procreate” course that now becomes a more than 10 hours length course that includes everything you need to dive into drawing on your iPad and grow as an artist from beginner to pro. You can find all the details about the course in my bio 👆
⠀
By the way, don’t forget to use BIRD code to get a 20% discount! 🎁
⠀
Also, I have an idea of creating a little collaboration with you. Create your own birds and share them using hashtags #procreatebird and #kunchevsky and then I will compose all of them into one big flock of birds. It should be fun! 🦅🐦🦢
⠀
Hope you like the idea! Looking forward to seeing your thoughts in the comments 💛

⠀

🔸 Gain the highest score in the leaderboards by this Sunday.

The sticker pack includes the game related stickers as well as a few stickers of my classic illustrations ✍️
⠀
On Sunday at 11AM (ET) I will announce the winners in my Instagram stories. Good luck! 🤗

Also, I would love to hear your feedback on the game, what is good and what is not. If the game survives I am planning to add so much more fun things to it. If you have any ideas I will appreciate if you share it in the comments 👇

News and free stickers (read till the end) 🔥
⠀
Hey guys! Haven’t done any personal posts in a while. Now after months of intense hard work and chaotic changes, I would like to share what’s been happening with me during past 6 months ☀️
⠀
As you might know I spent the most of this year in Bali, it was a really nice place to spend the quarantine at. While I was staying there I had some time to step back and think about my career and things I like do the most and the new things that I would like to do. And I figured out one thing that I was always passionate about but never had an opportunity to dive into it 🌊
⠀
So in May, I decided to start working on this new project. At first I dedicated  one hour a day to it (during a coffee break), then 2 hours a day and by July it became my 60-hours-a-week hobby 😄 And by August when I knew that soon I would go back home to my old routine I tried to do as much as I could to finish up that project ⚡️
⠀
I flew back home in the middle of August and only by now I’m ready to release that project. To be honest I’m really anxious about what the outcome will be 😅
⠀
Anyway, I hope you don’t mind me putting some mystery on what this project is, I will share all the details on Thursday. But now I’m wondering if anyone can guess what the project is about, first person who guesses it right will get my sticker pack! Please leave your guesses in the comments 👇
